data.description: Looking for a beautiful home in NISD? Look no further! Built in 2010 this home has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a 2 car garage! A large primary bedroom with primary bath features a jetted tub, separate shower, double sink vanity and a walk in closet! BRAND NEW carpet in all bedrooms and tile throughout living and kitchen area. Kitchen features granite-tile countertops, breakfast bar, pantry and plenty of storage. *Utilities inside, all appliances stay, never flooded, and fresh paint in practically every room* Enjoy the backyard with covered patio perfect for entertaining friends & family. Don't wait, schedule your tour today!
